Description:
    Create a chrome exrension boilerplate generator that creates everything for you. have fun.

Example:
    yeoman init chromeext $NAME[OPTIONAL]

    This will create:
        app/manifest.json
        app/background.js
        app/contentscript.js
        app/options.html
        app/popup.html
        app/icon-128.png
        app/icon-38.png
        app/icon-19.png
        app/icon-16.png
        app/styles/main.css
        app/_locales/en/messages.json
